Summer time is hitting us and the temperature keeps rising&hellip;
Instead of turning on your AC, prepare some bentos for the picnic and join this meetup to get some cool mist with us in a beautiful location.
There will be no specific structure to this meetup - except the usual introduction and ice breaking - but we will be happy to bring casual discussions about sustainability, food and the necessity of preserving the quality of the water around us.
